data.description: Beautiful home in Cumberland close to Hwy 6, 288, and Beltway 8. Only a short drive to down town Houston and an even shorter drive to Pearland or Sugar Land.Home was remodeled and converted from a 4 BR 2 Bath to a 3 BR 2 Bath. Very spacious with real wood cabinets, kitchen Island, dining area in kitchen, Granite counter tops, Beautiful Master upstairs, Open floor plan, Wood, tile, and wood laminate flooring. This house is a must see!
data.whatILove: It's been updated and was built well. The neighborhood is awesome and it's sooo close to everything!
